Rating: 2
this is a tasty, very light summer salad. i thought it might need a little extra punch so added twice as much garlic and some red pepper flakes to the shrimp. after tasting it, it could have used even more. next time i'll double the shrimp and snow peas and use less watercress (it was a little bitter and overpowering). i would also top it with some toasted sesame seeds.

Rating: 4
