Rating: 4
I was a little nervous about how this would taste but it was delicious! I doubled the amount of shrimp, walnuts, belgian endive and sauce. Ran out of white wine vinegar so used rice wine as well. Also, used sesame oil to cook the walnuts and snow peas. Pretty easy but there are multiple bowls to clean up after. Try it!

